d31a4012c78c4079444491e495c0febcd39e57f681935a25b6cf908cdf665ed1,bateman2011,sea_level_indicator,"Goukamma, Knysna Local Municipality, Garden Route District Municipality, Western Cape, South Africa",page_3_feature_1,-34.009784,22.9380759,inferred_text,5000.0,73.0,MSL,SRTM15+V2,submerged_beach,page OCR extracted from figure/table/map block,null,null,other,"The evolution of coastal barrier systems: a case study of the Middle-Late Pleistocene Wilderness barriers, South Africa","Goukamma, Knysna Local Municipality, Garden Route District Municipality, Western Cape, South Africa","The evolution of coastal barrier systems: a case study of the Middle-Late Pleistocene Wilderness barriers, South Africa",https://doi.org/10.1016/j.quascirev.2010.10.003,0.7,Extracted from page OCR block on page 3 with cue 'Fig. 2. Photographs of the Seaward barrier and its constituent sediment and sedimentary structures. (a) The Seaward barr' from source 'mineru_image'. Place name geocoded from query 'Goukamma'.,"{""page"": ""3"", ""figure"": ""Fig. 2. Photographs of the Seaward barrier and its constituent sediment and sedimentary structures. (a) The Seaward barr"", ""table"": null, ""section"": null, ""quote_or_paraphrase"": ""Fig. 2. Photographs of the Seaward barrier and its constituent sediment and sedimentary structures. (a) The Seaward barrier between Sedgefield and Gerickespunt (Site 9) which attains an elevation of over 180 m amsl. (b) Sea-cliffs at Gerickespunt eroded into the Seaward barrier revealing a complex internal architecture of stacked parabolic dunes with the bedding preserved in a pristine condition by the lithification of the sand into aeolianite (Site 9a). (c) Aeolianite exposure in the Seaward barrier at Sedgefield (near Site 17) illustrating preserved high-angle bedding (base) and a rhizolithic rich zone (top) indicating former palaeosols or palaeo-surfaces. (d) Extensive palaeosol developed on the surface of the aeolianite in the sea-cliffs in front of Groenvlei and buried by unconsolidat""}","{""reported_elevation_m"": null, ""reported_depth_m"": null, ""reported_datum"": null, ""reported_uncertainty_m"": null}","{""raw_raster_value_m"": 73.0, ""applied_correction_m"": null, ""derived_elevation_m"": 73.0, ""derived_depth_m"": null, ""derivation_notes"": ""Elevation sampled from SRTM15+V2 at inferred coordinates because source elevation was not reported. Treat this as approximate spatial context, not a surveyed sample elevation.""}","[{""method"": ""other"", ""relation"": ""unknown"", ""age_ka"": null, ""uncertainty_ka"": null, ""material"": null, ""notes"": ""No direct age model extracted from page OCR block.""}]",73,73,73,73
