fdabec7722faaf38a74915ddb065b7a5b5b1cc2119b3209eb1a17902de9b09f8,forbes2014,sea_level_indicator,"Point Deroche, Savage Harbour, Queen's County, Queens County, Prince Edward Island, Canada",page_8_feature_1,46.4314095,-62.9039822,inferred_text,10000.0,3.0,MSL,SRTM15+V2,submerged_beach,page OCR extracted from figure/table/map block,null,null,other,Coastal products of marine transgression in cold-temperate and high-latitude coastal-plain settings: Gulf of St Lawrence and Beaufort Sea,"Point Deroche, Savage Harbour, Queen's County, Queens County, Prince Edward Island, Canada",Coastal products of marine transgression in cold-temperate and high-latitude coastal-plain settings: Gulf of St Lawrence and Beaufort Sea,https://doi.org/10.1144/SP388.18,0.7,Extracted from page OCR block on page 8 with cue 'Fig. 6. North Shore of Prince Edward Island. (a) Beach and linear foredune near Point Deroche (in distance) with nearsho' from source 'mineru_image'. Place name geocoded from query 'Point Deroche'.,"{""page"": ""8"", ""figure"": ""Fig. 6. North Shore of Prince Edward Island. (a) Beach and linear foredune near Point Deroche (in distance) with nearsho"", ""table"": null, ""section"": null, ""quote_or_paraphrase"": ""Fig. 6. North Shore of Prince Edward Island. (a) Beach and linear foredune near Point Deroche (in distance) with nearshore ice complex protecting the beach from waves in open water to seaward (at left); note icefoot with windblown sand at base of beach; exceptional year with no snow cover (March 2000). (b) Tidal inlet at North Rustico, looking into the estuary, with nearshore ice complex in foreground over ebb delta; note groyne confining channel at right, narrow inlet throat and flood delta beyond (March 2000). (c) Foredune growth with sand accumulation and new ridge to seaward, Point Deroche; note surveyor for scale (July 1999). (d) Lag gravel and boulders on erosional profile at base of till cliff underlying high perched dune following a major storm, Brackley Beach; note figure on beach""}","{""reported_elevation_m"": null, ""reported_depth_m"": null, ""reported_datum"": null, ""reported_uncertainty_m"": null}","{""raw_raster_value_m"": 3.0, ""applied_correction_m"": null, ""derived_elevation_m"": 3.0, ""derived_depth_m"": null, ""derivation_notes"": ""Elevation sampled from SRTM15+V2 at inferred coordinates because source elevation was not reported. Treat this as approximate spatial context, not a surveyed sample elevation.""}","[{""method"": ""other"", ""relation"": ""unknown"", ""age_ka"": null, ""uncertainty_ka"": null, ""material"": null, ""notes"": ""No direct age model extracted from page OCR block.""}]",3,3,3,3
